{"tid":1363501,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"MOMO、定延未經JYP同意偷開直播 「娜璉剛洗完只穿浴袍」意外曝光嚇翻！","createTime":"2019-07-25T07:57:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-25T11:41:05.000Z","uid":74065,"like":17,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"0c4115cebf0c92ddbdc5a2b426279f5f4e6746fa","tid":1363501,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T07:57:17.000Z","msg":"韓團TWICE不只常分享生活或工作照，也常透過VLIVE開直播與粉絲互動，本身就較不按牌理出牌的成員定延和MOMO在24日就未經公司同意開直播，怎料卻意外讓娜璉私下最無修飾的一面曝光了！<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4260/d4260188.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4260%2Fd4260188.jpg&h=7d57961a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲定延和MOMO偷開直播。（圖／翻攝自TWICE VLIVE）<br />\n<br />\nTWICE在24日前往芝加哥舉辦演唱會，結束當晚定延和MOMO突然開了直播，標題寫著「瞞著公司偷開的VLIVE」，一開場定延就說：「我們瞞著公司的人沒說一聲就開了直播，（他們）現在一定嚇很大一跳吧。」但因為實在是太久沒透過直播與粉絲互動，她們比起擔心反而樂在其中。<br />\n<br />\nMOMO提到原本卸妝中想著「大家說要集合」結果一看手機就出現定延提議開直播的訊息，因此也只把眼妝卸掉就來了，一陣閒聊後突然聽到有人敲房門的聲音。MOMO興奮說「是成員才幫忙開門」，定延隨即拿著手機走到門邊，試圖想用門眼確認是誰但還是搞不清楚，怎料一打開竟然是剛洗完澡只穿著浴袍、毛巾包頭還敷著面膜的娜璉。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4260/4260189.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4260%2F4260189.jpg&h=f83b2450&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲娜璉不知道正在直播只穿著浴袍就來了。（圖／翻攝自TWICE VLIVE）<br />\n<br />\n娜璉原來還默默抱怨「不是說要集合嗎」，結果一看到手機在拍馬上嚇到緊急拿毛巾遮住臉大喊：「妳瘋了嗎？」定延充滿歉意又覺得不好意思地默默說：「看來娜璉姐姐不知道我們在直播。」經歷了一番驚喜她們3個人才好不容易聚在一起，但又馬上面對床後方的鏡子難關，好在定延和MOMO幫忙才順利讓娜璉只出現聲音打招呼。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NfauA1r.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNfauA1r.jpg&h=eb4fe31e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/k7Ng0s7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk7Ng0s7.jpg&h=62392b72&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EQRxyN7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEQRxyN7.png&h=3e809028&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"563a0c82fb5676cb682f8a0bf1477637327fc28b","tid":1363501,"uid":240447,"like":12,"dislike":2,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T07:57:50.000Z","msg":"哇屌撞鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55ca4f93d0db71cc5c189bf2fc9154cee3df88e9","tid":1363501,"uid":48577,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T08:13:23.000Z","msg":"好撚柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cebe5cda15daad1d0c27b0c06c70cb150dae5a0","tid":1363501,"uid":74065,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"563a0c82fb5676cb682f8a0bf1477637327fc28b","tid":1363501,"uid":240447,"like":12,"dislike":2,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T07:57:50.000Z","msg":"哇屌撞鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T08:13:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/R0pGsd1.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FR0pGsd1.gif&h=73dfe7c7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a122206aaa36908432fda48b44ea6b464b476737","tid":1363501,"uid":208486,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T08:14:46.000Z","msg":"璉登仔留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/45DTik8.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F45DTik8.gif&h=caaefa21&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/e8Bmseu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fe8Bmseu.jpg&h=a898fc0a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a3c840e07e7f88a180bf94c9f42aadeeb11cdd1b","tid":1363501,"uid":238483,"like":3,"dislike":6,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T08:21:12.000Z","msg":"點解冇左Mina仲可以玩得咁開心?"},{"pid":"e245089ac7591314dae074cbcbd39efe0721fcbc","tid":1363501,"uid":68678,"like":12,"